rows.name:
Friends not talk to Kajiji right now!
Kajiji busy with piloting!

rows.label: tlk42360111_01_msg0002
rows.name:
For Divine Beast to fly in sky, need ether
energy produced from Cloud Sea!

rows.label: tlk42360111_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But if lower altitude too much, Divine Beast
get attacked by Cloud Sea monsters.

rows.label: tlk42360111_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Need to maintain altitude low enough
to achieve good speed, but not so low
to get attack by monster.

rows.label: tlk42360111_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Piloting require many intricate
technique to maintain fine balance!
